OL,5, A 16-year-old boy lost thousands of    
OL,6, pounds gambling in just a few weeks    
OL,7, after seeing adverts at a football     
OL,8, game, a support worker has said.       
OL,10,FNick Phillips, from Swansea, said the  
OL,11,Fboy opened an account in his father's  
OL,12,Fname an hour after a match.            
OL,14,FWelsh MPs and anti-gambling charities  
OL,15,Fare calling for the UK government to   
OL,16,Fpublish its gambling white paper, which
OL,17,Fhad been expected before the summer.   
OL,19,FThe UK government said it was          
OL,20,Fdetermined to reduce gambling harm.    
